  <h1>Security</h1>
  <p>On this page, you can manage the access permissions of groups or people to documents stored in a selected document folder.</p>
  <p>Options:</p>
  <ul>
  <li><strong>Command Panel</strong>
  <ul>
  <li><strong>Add permissions</strong> - create a new document folder.</li>
  <li><strong>Edit</strong> - edit the selected permission.</li>
  <li><strong>Remove</strong> - permanently remove the selected permission.</li>
  </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>Permissions table</strong> - contains a list of defined permissions for the document folder. You can <a href="../../../../../../alvao-asset-management/working-with-tables">customize the table as needed</a>.</li>
  </ul>
</asp:Content>
